 "remarks": "New Price- Experience the best of downtown living in this spacious, sun-filled 2-bedroom, 2-bath residence offering approximately 1,525 square feet of thoughtfully designed space.   Originally configured as a 3-bedroom, this unit has been reimagined to create an expansive open-concept kitchen and dining area, perfect for both everyday living and entertaining. Enjoy an oversized balcony with beautiful sunset views, adding the perfect outdoor extension to your living space. Both bedrooms offer generous proportions, easily accommodating king-sized beds, along with a walk-in closet and additional storage.   This full-service building features a doorman, fitness center, garage parking, ample guest parking, a private storage unit, and an outdoor patio area ideal for relaxing or entertaining. Common charges include heat, hot water, and central air for added convenience. Ideally located in the heart of downtown, just moments from restaurants, shopping, and nightlife, with easy access to I-95 and the Merritt Parkway.",
